---
name: quality-report
version: 1.0.0
description: Final QA closeout report template for PASS verdicts.
format: markdown
required_variables:
  - generated_at
  - qa_pass
  - sprint_id
  - task_id
  - branch
  - commit
  - pr_number
  - verdict
  - validated_scope_md
  - findings_blocking
  - findings_important
  - findings_minor
  - residual_risks_md
  - merge_readiness
  - merge_reason
  - recommendation
optional_variables:
  - blocking_ids_json
  - reviewer_spawn_gate
  - reviewer_manifest_json
  - evidence_chain_json
defaults:
  blocking_ids_json: "[]"
  reviewer_spawn_gate: ""
  reviewer_manifest_json: "[]"
  evidence_chain_json: "{}"
---
# Final Quality Report

Generated: {{ generated_at }}
QA Pass: {{ qa_pass }}
Sprint/Task: {{ sprint_id }} / {{ task_id }}
Branch: `{{ branch }}`
Commit: `{{ commit }}`
PR: #{{ pr_number }}
Final Verdict: **{{ verdict }}**

## Machine Status (JSON)
```json
{
  "sprint": "{{ sprint_id }}",
  "task": "{{ task_id }}",
  "branch": "{{ branch }}",
  "commit": "{{ commit }}",
  "pr": {{ pr_number }},
  "verdict": "{{ verdict }}",
{% if reviewer_spawn_gate -%}
  "reviewer_spawn_gate": "{{ reviewer_spawn_gate }}",
  "reviewer_manifest": {{ reviewer_manifest_json }},
  "aggregation_source": "reviewer_fenced_json_union_todo_scan",
{% endif -%}
{% if evidence_chain_json and evidence_chain_json != "{}" -%}
  "evidence_chain": {{ evidence_chain_json }},
{% endif -%}
  "findings": {
    "blocking": {{ findings_blocking }},
    "important": {{ findings_important }},
    "minor": {{ findings_minor }}
  },
  "blocking_ids": {{ blocking_ids_json }},
  "merge_readiness": "{{ merge_readiness }}",
  "merge_reason": "{{ merge_reason }}",
  "next_action": "none",
  "owner": "none",
  "recommendation": "{{ recommendation }}"
}
```

## Validated Scope
{% if validated_scope_md -%}
{{ validated_scope_md }}
{% else -%}
- not specified
{% endif %}

## Findings Summary (Final)
{% if reviewer_spawn_gate -%}
- Reviewer spawn gate: **{{ reviewer_spawn_gate }}**
{% endif -%}
- Blocking: {{ findings_blocking }}
- Important: {{ findings_important }}
- Minor: {{ findings_minor }}

{% if reviewer_spawn_gate -%}
## Reviewer Manifest
```json
{{ reviewer_manifest_json }}
```
{% endif -%}

{% if evidence_chain_json and evidence_chain_json != "{}" -%}
## Evidence Chain
```json
{{ evidence_chain_json }}
```
{% endif -%}

## Residual Risks
{% if residual_risks_md -%}
{{ residual_risks_md }}
{% else -%}
- none
{% endif %}

## Merge Readiness
- Status: **{{ merge_readiness }}**
- Reason: {{ merge_reason }}

## Recommendation
{{ recommendation }}
